      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/31b6dce4-755d-11e1-bfc7-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
