      },
      "date": "2012-04-30 01:54:20.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThis looks good, but I think this patch has a high chance of merging problems bcause the patch it depends on could not be merged automatically.\nPerhaps it's a good idea to rebase this one as well?",
